<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l14"><expan>gnedıgſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / Daran er ſchreıbt vnd begert / daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> freẅnd </ab>
