<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> uns ist ein brief geantwurt worden von dem
                                <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan><expan>durlewchtigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        fürsten und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sig<ex>mund,</ex></expan>
<expan>römisch<ex>em</ex></expan> und zu <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc.
                        künig, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> daran er schreibt und begert, daz
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> frewnd von Sweinfurt, ir und wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> treffenlich
                            <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu dem
                            <expan>co<ex>n</ex>cilii</expan> gen Costencz senden
                                    <add><expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>, als ir das an der
                                <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>iefs,</ex></expan> die wir ewch hierinn
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en,</ex></expan> wol finden <expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan>.
                        Darnach wisse sich ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> ze
                                <expan>richt<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Francisci. </ab>
</div>
